    {
      "id": "4375e188-b391-45f2-bac8-af179092e9e0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose a Neural Network arquitecture that may be capable iof predictiong student performance without using personal sensitive information. Authors use OULAD for the purpose. Results on multiple relevant metrics are shown.",
